{"type": "article", "id": 17369, "title": "彩色积木沙发", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-11T06:34:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115208Yr0dm9vHTbqyM348.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这些沙发看上去完全是一组积木，有鲜艳的颜色和几何图案的造型。所有沙发都有穿孔，用黄色的带子将它们搭配组合，然后捆起来固定。它们可以组合成不同长短的沙发或者是床，也可以将单个拿出当做茶几，甚至没有重复的颜色，让你置身于自己搭建的城堡中。是一个能保持童心的组合。<a href=\"http://www.tijsgilde.com/array.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144440rd9gfvuMSkbD5QwC.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614444178abJdiLx0gOk6NB.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261444418R4DSnQZKz5xCW9u.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144442cmebYkyFHVK06GMO.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}